{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/cookie-policy/","result":{"data":{"wpPage":{"content":"\n<p>Last updated March 19, 2021<br>This Cookie Notice explains how TripleLift uses cookies to recognize you when you visit our website at triplelift.com (our “Website”). </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cookies and similar tracking technologie like pixels may be used for a variety of&nbsp; different purposes, including to make our Website function properly, to analyze how our Website is used, to count the number of visitors and to learn how the Website may be improved. Other cookies also enable us to track and target the interests of our users to enhance the experience on our Website.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The specific types of cookies served through our Website and the purposes they perform are described in the table below:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Cookie Name</strong></td><td><strong>Domain</strong></td><td><strong>Provider</strong></td><td><strong>Contents</strong></td><td><strong>Purpose</strong></td><td><strong>Type &amp; Lifetime</strong></td></tr><tr><td>__hssc</td><td>*.triplelift.com</td><td>HubSpot</td><td>Dynamic string (e.g. 246217115.8.1615498724184)</td><td>Analytics cookie which keeps track of sessions</td><td>30 minutes; persistent</td></tr><tr><td>__hssrc</td><td>*.triplelift.com</td><td>HubSpot</td><td>Static integer (e.g. 1)</td><td>Analytics cookie which is set to determine if the visitor has restarted their browser whenever HubSpot changes the session cookie</td><td>Session cookie</td></tr><tr><td>__hstc</td><td>*.triplelift.com</td><td>HubSpot</td><td>Dynamic string (e.g. 246217115.3925edb5c298d932ed4ec7a7fb166bee.1615496126882.1615496126882.1615498724184.2)</td><td>Analytics cookie which is the main cookie for tracking visitors</td><td>13 months; persistent</td></tr><tr><td>_fbp</td><td>*.triplelift.com</td><td>Facebook</td><td>Dynamic string (e.g. fb.1.1615496126730.1056365518)</td><td>Cookie which is used to personalise content (including ads), measure ads, produce analytics and provide a safer experience</td><td>90 days; persistent&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>_ga</td><td>*.triplelift.com</td><td>Google Analytics</td><td>Static, unique, string (e.g. GA1.2.553234263.1615496127)</td><td>Cookie which is used to distinguish users</td><td>2 years; persistent</td></tr><tr><td>_gcl_au</td><td>*.triplelift.com</td><td>Google Analytics</td><td>Dynamic string (e.g. 1.1.780208274.1615496127)</td><td>Cookie which is used to measure ad and campaign performance and conversion rates</td><td>90 days; persistent</td></tr><tr><td>_gid</td><td>*.triplelift.com</td><td>Google Analytics</td><td>Static, unique, string (e.g. GA1.2.2101257892.1615496127)</td><td>Cookie which is used to distinguish users</td><td>24 hours; persistent</td></tr><tr><td>hubspotutk</td><td>*.triplelift.com</td><td>HubSpot</td><td>Static, random, unique string (e.g. 3925edb5c298d932ed4ec7a7fb166bee)</td><td>Analytics cookie which keeps track of a visitor&#8217;s identity; passed to HubSpot on form submission and used when deduplicating contacts</td><td>13 months; persistent</td></tr><tr><td>NID</td><td>*.google.com</td><td>Google</td><td>Unique ID</td><td>Cookie which is used to maintain a user’s preferences</td><td>6 months; persistent</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n","title":"TripleLift.com Cookie Notice","slug":"cookie-policy","uri":"/cookie-policy/","isFrontPage":false,"isPrivacyPage":false,"PageCreativeGallery":{"pageHeading":null,"pageSubheading":null,"topHeading":null,"topSubheading":null},"PageProductOffers":{"headline":"Product Offers","leftHeader":null,"sliderProductOffer":null},"template":{"templateName":"Default"}}},"pageContext":{"uri":"/cookie-policy/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["492585110","848497233"]}